data.description: OPEN HOUSE - Sunday, Jan. 28th, 12:00p - 3:00p! This warm and welcoming home is conveniently located less than a mile of IH-35 and Creekside Shopping Center! The open-floor living and dining room concept connects with a charming archway. Kitchen showcases custom wood cabinets and a breakfast bar. Primary suite is split from the other bedrooms, and is equipped with dual vanities, a walk-in shower and a large closet. Fresh coats of paint enhance the backside of the home, which leads to an oversized, covered patio perfect for entertaining!
